ably avoid the use of products containing ginkgo biloba.', 'Synergism', 'Patients should consult a healthcare provider before taking any herbal or alternative medicine.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/119768/', '', 'St. John''s Wort, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Tryptophan, Esketamine', 'Rivastigmine, Galantamine, Donepezil, Tacrine, Memantine, Aducanumab', 1767369485);
